nodes.text: Dictio L'varren was a male Human who served as the New Republic ambassador to the Indu San system.

Kella Rand had an encounter with L'varren on the planet of Corellia. Approximately a year later on Indu San, she turned in evidence to L'varren, incriminating Kaleb Darme in the assassination of Shek Barayel, chief councilor of the Indu San system.
